---
layout: base
nav: writing
seoTitle: "writing — a quiet room"
ogTitle: "writing — a quiet room"
description: "Notes, thoughts, and journal entries from a quiet room."
---
<main class="wrap">
  <p class="eyebrow" data-reveal="0">writing</p>
  <h1 class="title" data-reveal="1" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.25rem); margin-top: 1rem;">from the quiet</h1>
  <p class="lede" data-reveal="2" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
    Thoughts set down before they drift away.
  </p>

  <ul class="entries">
    {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
    <li class="entry" data-reveal="{{ loop.index0 + 3 }}">
      <a href="{{ post.url }}">
        <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      </a>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>

  <a href="/" class="back">back to the door</a>
</main>
